WEBVTT

00:00:28.791 --> 00:00:30.972
from their own farm.

00:00:30.972 --> 00:00:34.900
One goro goro can feed three meals

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:36.881
for an average family,

00:00:36.881 --> 00:00:39.970
and in 1984, the whole harvest

00:00:39.970 --> 00:00:43.142
could fit in one goro goro.

00:00:43.142 --> 00:00:45.992
It was and still is one of the worst droughts

00:00:45.992 --> 00:00:48.635
in living memory.

00:00:48.635 --> 00:00:51.594
Now today, I insure farmers against droughts

00:00:51.594 --> 00:00:53.655
like those in the year of the cup,

00:00:53.655 --> 00:00:58.641
or to be more specific, I insure the rains.

00:00:58.641 --> 00:01:01.090
I come from a family of missionaries